Provide assistance and advice in meeting the practical needs of the science curriculum, including liaising with teaching staff and support staff outside the Science Faculty;
Ensure the availability of suitable materials and equipment by compiling orders and liaising or negotiating with suppliersand finance office;
Keep up-to-date stock records;
